data.description: This charming open floor plan is flooded with natural light, creating a beautifully bright ambiance. As you step onto the front patio, you're greeted by an inviting living room that offers generous space. The Master bedroom is very spacious and features its own private bathroom. This unit is packed with desirable features, including tandem parking for two vehicles and an additional storage unit. Peachtree Orleans is a hidden gem in Buckhead, tucked away on Peachtree Road, conveniently near Phipps Plaza and Lenox Square. It's truly Buckhead's best-kept secret. Within this secure gated community, residents can delight in amenities such as a saltwater swimming pool, a pleasant picnic area, and delightful courtyards featuring gas lanterns. The location also ensures easy reach to GA 400 and convenient shopping options at Target and Publix, catering to all your shopping requirements.
